OL,3,CRestaurant owner: 'Find hero who saved
OL,4,Cmy worker's life from burning building'
OL,6,FA restaurant owner in Birmingham is
OL,7,Fcalling on the public to help him find
OL,8,Fthe person who rescued his employee
OL,9,Ffrom their burning building, after
OL,10,Fthey climbed in to get him out from
OL,11,Fthe flames.
OL,13,FA fire broke out at Shababs Balti
OL,14,FRestaurant on Sunday morning (22
OL,15,FJune). Ramess Ponmagar, the worker,
OL,16,Fwas trapped on the first floor at the
OL,17,Ftime.
