OL,3,CRestaurant owner: 'Find hero who saved
OL,4,Cmy worker's life from burning building'
OL,6,FRamess said he managed to seek help by
OL,7,Fhitting the window with the chair and
OL,8,Fencouraging neighbours outside to
OL,9,Fsmash the windows with stones and
OL,10,Fbricks.
OL,12,FHe was rescued by the walking passer-
OL,13,Fby, assisted by neighbours, and was
OL,14,Fthen taken to hospital.
OL,16,FHe said: "It was very scary, I
OL,17,Fthought, I'm going to die."
OL,19,F"It was just a heroic moment"
