OL,3,CRestaurant owner: 'Find hero who saved
OL,4,Cmy worker's life from burning building'
OL,6,FThe restaurant owner Zafar Hussain is
OL,7,Fnow looking to trace the man who
OL,8,Fhelped rescue his employee, but who
OL,9,Fleft the scene, calling him a "hero".
OL,11,FHe said: "Members of the public were
OL,12,Fbeginning to throw stones and bricks
OL,13,Fat the window to try and smash it
OL,14,Fthrough for him to escape.
OL,16,F"It wasn't successful but another
OL,17,Fbrave member of public who got a
OL,18,Fladder from next door, put it up
OL,19,Fagainst the building, climbed up,
OL,20,Fsmashed the window and got him out.
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4          G3/5
