OL,3,CRestaurant owner: 'Find hero who saved
OL,4,Cmy worker's life from burning building'
OL,6,F"It was just a heroic moment and i'd
OL,7,Flike to express my thanks and
OL,8,Fgratitude to this person and I'd like
OL,9,Fthem to come forward for me to
OL,10,Fpersonally thank them for saving this
OL,11,Fperson's life."
OL,13,FThe restaurant plans to reopen on
OL,14,FFriday evening, with limited capacity.
OL,16,FThey have two kitchens - their second
OL,17,Fone was protected by fire doors which
OL,18,Fmeans it is still functioning.
